## 🛠 API Reference

All responses follow the shape:
```json
{ "success": true/false, "message": "...", "data": ... }
```

### Auth
| Method | Endpoint                    | Auth     | Description          |
|--------|-----------------------------|----------|----------------------|
| POST   | /api/auth/register          | —        | Register citizen     |
| POST   | /api/auth/login             | —        | Login (returns JWT)  |
| GET    | /api/auth/me                | 🔒 Any   | Get own profile      |
| PUT    | /api/auth/profile           | 🔒 Any   | Update profile       |
| PUT    | /api/auth/change-password   | 🔒 Any   | Change password      |

### Complaints
| Method | Endpoint                        | Auth            | Description                    |
|--------|---------------------------------|-----------------|--------------------------------|
| GET    | /api/complaints/track/:id       | —               | Public tracking by ID or CP-no |
| POST   | /api/complaints                 | 🔒 Citizen      | Submit complaint (+ image)     |
| GET    | /api/complaints/my              | 🔒 Citizen      | My complaints                  |
| POST   | /api/complaints/:id/feedback    | 🔒 Citizen      | Rate resolved complaint        |
| GET    | /api/complaints/assigned        | 🔒 Officer      | Complaints assigned to me      |
| PUT    | /api/complaints/:id/status      | 🔒 Officer/Admin| Update status + resolution     |
| GET    | /api/complaints                 | 🔒 Admin        | All complaints (filterable)    |
| PUT    | /api/complaints/:id/assign      | 🔒 Admin        | Assign officer                 |
| DELETE | /api/complaints/:id             | 🔒 Admin        | Delete complaint               |
| GET    | /api/complaints/:id             | 🔒 Any          | Get single with timeline       |

#### Query params for GET /api/complaints
```
?status=open|progress|resolved|closed
&priority=low|medium|high
&category=roads|water|sanitation|electricity|parks|other
&zone_id=1
&department_id=1
&search=pothole
&page=1&limit=20
```

### Analytics (Admin / Officer)
| Method | Endpoint                            | Description                    |
|--------|-------------------------------------|--------------------------------|
| GET    | /api/analytics/overview             | KPI cards (totals, SLA, avg)   |
| GET    | /api/analytics/monthly-trend        | Last 12 months bar chart data  |
| GET    | /api/analytics/by-category          | Breakdown by category          |
| GET    | /api/analytics/heatmap              | Zone-wise density map data     |
| GET    | /api/analytics/leaderboard          | Department ranking             |
| GET    | /api/analytics/sla-violations       | Active SLA breaches            |
| GET    | /api/analytics/predictive           | AI-style trend insights        |

### Departments
| Method | Endpoint                        | Auth    |
|--------|---------------------------------|---------|
| GET    | /api/departments                | —       |
| GET    | /api/departments/:id            | —       |
| POST   | /api/departments                | Admin   |
| PUT    | /api/departments/:id            | Admin   |
| DELETE | /api/departments/:id            | Admin   |

### Zones
| Method | Endpoint            | Auth  |
|--------|---------------------|-------|
| GET    | /api/zones          | —     |
| PUT    | /api/zones/:id/risk | Admin |

### Users (Admin)
| Method | Endpoint                    |
|--------|-----------------------------|
| GET    | /api/users                  |
| POST   | /api/users/officer          |
| PATCH  | /api/users/:id/toggle       |

### Notifications
| Method | Endpoint                    |
|--------|-----------------------------|
| GET    | /api/notifications          |
| PATCH  | /api/notifications/read-all |
| PATCH  | /api/notifications/:id/read |

### SLA Rules (Admin)
| Method | Endpoint        |
|--------|-----------------|
| GET    | /api/sla        |
| PUT    | /api/sla/:id    |

---

## 🗄 Database Schema

**Tables:** `users` · `departments` · `zones` · `complaints` · `complaint_timeline` · `sla_rules` · `notifications`

**Roles:** `citizen` · `officer` · `admin`

**Complaint statuses:** `open` → `progress` → `resolved` → `closed`

---

## 🔐 Authentication

All protected routes require:
```
Authorization: Bearer <jwt_token>
```

Tokens expire in 7 days (configurable via `JWT_EXPIRES_IN`).

---

## 📦 Tech Stack

- **Runtime:** Node.js
- **Framework:** Express.js 4.x
- **Database:** MySQL 8 via `mysql2`
- **Auth:** JWT (`jsonwebtoken`) + bcrypt (`bcryptjs`)
- **Upload:** Multer (local disk, max 10 MB)
- **Validation:** express-validator
- **Dev:** nodemon
